	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Heh... I think it's a great idea.  Why you might ask?  Well because I kinda posted on this exact topic a long arse time ago as to how to get AA sinks that could cost a ton of AA and yet keep improving us as a class.  Now Blazz, maybe folks just like you more but I got about 10 neg rep bumbs when I posted this idea so you might get the same... but not from me <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
<br />
I love this idea.  Look at any of the classes and how easy it is to max out the "important" AA.  I know so many of my friends that are working up their Charisma, Wis, Int AAs because they have all the needed ones, along with resists and what not.  It's impressive but not jaw dropping to hear that folks have maxed AAs now days.  Considering the xp in the EP, which I've just gotten access to and is INSANE to get 7AA in a relaxing night of grinding with my guildies.<br />
<br />
Anyway, I still agree we need some powerful AA that we can dump a ton of points into but give us a noticeable return.</p>
	
	
	
